Definition: fleshy maritime plant having fleshy stems with rudimentary scalelike leaves and small spikes of minute flowers
Example: formerly used in making glass
Synonyms: samphire, Salicornia_europaea, herb, genus_Salicornia, m, fleshy, maritime, plant, having, stems, with, rudimentary, scalelike, leaves, and, small, spikes, of, minute, flowers, formerly, used, in, making, glass
Category: noun.plant
